** ObjectState refcount
  - DataStoreFrontend.loadObject always does an incref and NO decref
  - each read/operation that uses loadObject must do their own decref
     |-> You're loading it for a reason so decref when done with it
  - otherwise there's a race condition for loss

** Need decref at end of DataStoreFrontend.rebuild process

